text: Maria is the first single by international boy band US5. == Charts == This is the only single which reached number 1 in Germany and 6 in the Billboard Hot 100. == Music Video == The video shows that the members sing to different girls in different places. At the end, Lou sent those girls to where the members are and showed the planet with the name of the band like how Universal Studios did their logo. Category:2005 songs
title: Maria (US5 song)
